quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"Min njippini ii mbo e jehma leylatul qadiri."
  97,2,"Holko anndinat ma leylatul qadiri."
  97,3,"Leylatu qadri oon ɓuri ujunere lewru moƴƴude."
  97,4,"Maleykaaji na telloo wond'ude e jibriil e sakkitoore joom mu'en e kala yamiroore."
  97,5,"Kombo kisal tan ha fajiri feera."
